import { Flex, Box, Text, Center } from '@chakra-ui/react'

const heading = {
  fontSize: 48,
  fontWeight: 700,
  textAlign: 'left' as const,

  color: 'space_cadet',
  pl: '1%'
}

const center = {
  fontSize: 24,
  fontWeight: 200,
  textAlign: 'center' as const,
  color: 'ultra_violet',
  w: '33%',
  pt: '50%',
}

export default function Heading() {
  return (
    <Flex height='50px'>
      <Box w='50%' h='100%'>
        <Text {...heading} >Ari Wisenburn</Text>
      </Box>
      <Box flex='1'>
        <Flex>
          <Center {...center}>
            Projects
          </Center>
          <Center {...center}>
            Contact
          </Center>
          <Center {...center}>
            Download Resume
          </Center>
        </Flex>
      </Box>
    </Flex >
  )
}
